Price Enterprises to split into 2 companies . Price Enterprises Inc said Wednesday it will restructure by splitting its real estate and merchandising businesses into two separate publicly - traded companies . After the restructuring , Price Enterprises will consist of the real estate operations and will be positioned to convert into a real estate investment trust ( REIT ) . The merchandising business , to be named PriceSmart , is expected to be distributed as a special dividend on August 29 , or shortly thereafter . The company said splitting into two will have strategic benefits for both divisions . 
